*[[ἄγγελος]] / aggelos / ang'-el-os
=== Etymology ===

*From ἀγγέλλω aggellō (probably derived from G71; compare G34; to bring tidings); a messenger; especially an “angel”; by implication a pastor: - angel, messenger.